<SP>
<SPEAKER><HI>Mi&s;s</HI> LOVELESS [<HI>in great joy.</HI>]</SPEAKER>
<P>Thank you! thank you! dear papa! I wi&s;h you joy, my good <HI>Cartwright;</HI> my &s;econd mother.</P>
